Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉 克劳迪娅 西蒙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不嫌弃的话就和我商量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别当真 是这家伙瞎编的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就尽管这么想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总有一天 世界会臣服于我的脚下!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 原来流行那样的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12点左右…坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理他们说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:06.59,Default_tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中钵博士 见面会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见面会中止?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧瀬红莉栖 事件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我所看到的都是幻觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 约翰·提托?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:39.16,Default_tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间旅行者登场www
