Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要破坏由SERN创造的绝望乡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新夺回自由
