Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:23.04,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx100)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:22.83,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300, 300)}多世界解释。量子论方法中比较有名的两种解释之一。\N与哥本哈根解释不同，主张分裂的是整个世界。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(974,424)}也就是说 是多重世界说?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 时间并不是由过去流向未来的唯一直线
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是像河流一样 由无数条平行的「世界线」构成的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说 今天你被杀人魔杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而来自未来的我却说这是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为世界已经分成了你被杀和没被杀两支
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的提托是日本人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2000年左右 在美国网络上出现的 自称时间旅行者的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是从2036年而来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为拯救未来的世界而进行了时间旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时在网络上引起一阵热议
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还出了好几本相关的书
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没想现在还有自称约翰·提托的笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来通过这个链接调查下提托去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桶子这混蛋 居然把提托的链接给删掉了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有12个结果?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.48,0:13:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说已经过了10年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但当时可是引起了巨大的骚动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相关的书应该都放在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 桶子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在正和菲利斯碳快乐地…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:53.54,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书放哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 什么书?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关约翰·提托的书
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书不是整理好了都放在一起的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰·提托
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我几乎通宵调查了关于约翰·提托的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运用网上搜索的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能地搜集了信息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望提托能回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前 也就是2000年的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说了很有意思的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 很遗憾 我并没有去过2000年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时也没有这个打算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wait wait wait
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚拍了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:15:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你的人身安全 立刻删掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果让你留下了不愉快的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在拍什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己…今天…走过哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够古董的电脑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你了解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有清楚的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许 桶子的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把照片删掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我…那个人的…邮箱地址
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要威胁我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉我的话 我就删掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 我也不能出卖同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能告诉你我的邮箱地址
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是写着是凤凰院凶真么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我发条空信息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你回信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工时是真由喜喵喵啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 「冈伦」和「欢迎回来」发音挺像的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桶子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在里面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶真?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你好久了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天露一次面的约定你忘哪去了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 机关的妨碍十分严重…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵喵 机关居然已经逼到那种地步了吗喵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.53,0:17:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么今天也是为了打倒机关的机密会议?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:13.36,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(729,660)}Stealth Field
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请带我去隐蔽力场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到喵 菲利斯也想参加啊喵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 机关没有弱到连你都能对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 菲利斯我可是有禁断的秘奥义的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你已经掌握了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是这个难道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺过了圭亚那高原的修行 经历过了师父的死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利斯终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我发短信跟你说的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得跟人生赢家组说话就输了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对满嘴谎言的女人没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的「你没资格说」帖子就放这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 你个花心混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:17:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2次元的老婆们在哭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利斯炭不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她同时属于2次元和3次元!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不提了 你倒是先来帮我看看这张照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:11.13,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300, 300)}IBN
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:11.34,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx100)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:11.13,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300, 300)}美国的电脑企业。不仅进行硬件软件的开发和贩卖，\N还进行面向企业的维护服务、指导推销等业务。而且\N近些年来后者开始成为主要业务。在ＰＣ上开发的\N操作系统、硬盘、软盘等等也使其闻名遐迩。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 这个不是IBN5100吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IBN?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦幻的老式PC
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概一个月前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有传言说它就沉睡在秋叶原的某个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这恐怕是听说之后来打听的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来也没找到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:28.31,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300, 300)}疾风迅雷的Night HALT
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:28.52,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx100)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:28.31,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300, 300)}Chaos;Head的主人公、西条拓巳在MMORPG\N「Empire Sweeper Online」中使用的角色「Night HALT」的通称。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西甚至还把「疾风迅雷的Night HALT」都给惹来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:33.73,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300, 300)}Final Answer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:34.03,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx100)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:33.73,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300, 300)}确认「也就是说这就是最终的结论了，是不是?」\N的时候常常会使用的网络俗语。来源是一个只要答对全部问题就能够\N获得１０００万円的人气问答节目。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终却得出了「找不到就是不存在」的Final Answer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是这么贵重的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发售时间距今有30年以上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时因为价格关系 谁都买不起PC
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就变得超级稀有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那个女人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就发信息给你了 我是桐生萌郁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35}发信人：闪光的指压师\N标题：我等你\N凤凰院先生，这就发信息给你了。\N我是桐生萌郁。\N我叫桐生萌郁!二十岁!!自由职业者!!!\N以后再给你发邮件也没问题吧!?\N就算你说不要我也会发的\N萌郁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十岁 自由职业者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你说不要我也会发的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:19:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和刚刚那女人是同一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸亏没有出卖你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是贵重的PC 很有可能并不在秋叶原
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,El Psy Congroo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 久等了喵喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界糟糕了出现了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:22.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃 真好吃啊这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:25.74,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃点喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大学实验室进行分析的结果表明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胶蕉在分子层面上已经支离破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说香蕉已经变成了其他的东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不糟糕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据现状能想到的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是受到了电话烤箱（暂定）电磁波的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据是?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科学狂人的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说毫无根据
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:19:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 连接完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 那么就用它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.64,0:20:11.06,Default_tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香蕉：真由喜的。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不是真由氏的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是{\i1}我{\i0} 用真由理提供的研究经费买的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才说这是真由氏的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:14.69,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 把一整串都扔进去确认下变化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:16.48,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300, 300)}常考
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:16.48,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx100)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:16.48,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300, 300)}通常考虑的简称
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一根就够了吧 常考
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这么点就能确认电话烤箱（暂定）的真正力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.62,0:20:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个括号暂定罗嗦 赶紧去掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在实验上这么小气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是无法改变世界格局的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想改变的也只有你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香蕉消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:04.74,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(902,660)}Cooling Off
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 紧急要求666 立刻发动冷严之封印
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府的批准? 现在是说这事的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自演 辛苦了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你藏哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你藏起来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:20.47,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(727,660)}Teleport
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这说不定是能够进行瞬间转移的电子烤箱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…怎么可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.89,0:21:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又该如何说明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那一串香蕉上摘下 放到烤箱里的香蕉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胶…蕉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 它是不是完整地接上了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚的确摘了一根吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.91,0:21:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大概
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:53.21,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(750,660)}Teleport
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这果然…是瞬间转移
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做很有趣的实验呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:21:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部伦太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.84,0:22:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 是叫凤凰院凶真来着?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧瀬…红莉栖


Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.01,0:22:10.01,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------- ED first non-black frame -------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:27.82,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規制された視界 無慈悲なる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.19,0:22:36.58,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二の支配 逃れられない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:45.00,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安息の明日を願った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:54.14,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手の中の尊い事象の地平へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.34,0:23:02.94,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囚われし盟約 現れた偽証の輪郭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.10,0:23:12.07,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命の天地は盲目な時間を刻んで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:17.08,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽ばたけバタフライ 奇跡のバタフライ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.45,0:23:20.96,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたへ捧ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:25.34,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙のバタフライ 眩しいバタフライ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.85,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全てが 今書き換えられる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:27.82,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被限制的视界 毫无慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.19,0:22:36.58,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二条的支配 无从逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:45.00,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾祈求安息的明日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:54.14,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去向手中珍贵现象的地平线
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.34,0:23:02.94,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被囚禁的盟约 出现的伪证轮廓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.10,0:23:12.07,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命的天地即铭刻于盲目的时间之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:17.08,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振翅高飞吧蝴蝶 奇迹的蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.45,0:23:20.96,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向你奉献一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:25.34,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪水闪耀的蝴蝶 炫目的蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.85,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 能将一切重写
